#. 2: sound
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: sound
#. 6: pause (longer)
#. 7: pause (long)
msgctxt "Talk22"
msgid ""
"<1.so>\"When a dark light resides in the cursed\n"
"statue's eyes, pierce its gaze to purge\n"
"the seal from the shrine.\"\n"
"<2.so>I've been pondering the <3.se_co>dark light<4.re_co>\n"
"mentioned here for some time, and I\n"
"must admit I'm stumped.\n"
"<5.so>Light can't be dark, obviously. Unless...<6.pa>\n"
"Whoops!<7.pa> Can't go divulging my research\n"
"before I publish, now, can I?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "near00"
msgid "What a mystery..."
msgstr ""

