#. 3: raw
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk24"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I only do fieldwork at shrines and ruins\n"
"during the day.<2.pa> Why, you ask?<3.ra>Hmm, could it have something to "
"do\n"
"with the hordes of monsters roaming at\n"
"night? <4.pa>What an ignoramus..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk25"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I try not to set foot outside my hut when\n"
"night falls and monsters begin to roam\n"
"this area.\n"
"Just because I'm a trained archaeologist\n"
"doesn't mean I have any skill with\n"
"a blade. Quite the opposite, in fact."
msgstr ""

