msgctxt "talk27"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hrm...<2.pa> This changes things...<3.ra><4.so><5.so>Very well "
"then!<6.pa> I'm feeling charitable,\n"
"so I'll let a few things spill.<7.pa> This is just\n"
"between us, understand.\n"
"\"When a dark light resides in the cursed\n"
"statue's eyes, pierce its gaze to purge\n"
"the seal from the shrine.\"<8.pa>\n"
"<9.so>I'm still in the process of deciphering\n"
"that one, so I don't suppose there's\n"
"any harm in sharing it with you.\n"
"That's my life in a nutshell.<10.pa> Days filled\n"
"with researching shrines and nights\n"
"spent studying ancient texts.\n"
"That leaves no time to converse with\n"
"passing strangers, so farewell."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound2
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "talk29"
msgid ""
"<1.so><2.so>I mustn't be outside right now!\n"
"My glasses are unfortunately metallic,\n"
"so I must remain indoors at all costs!<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: text_size
#. 2: sound
#. 3: raw
#. 4: pause (longer)
#. 5: pause (long)
#. 6: text_size
msgctxt "talk30"
msgid ""
"<1.te_si><2.so>A shrine? Here? But I hadn't completed my\n"
"inquiry into the mystery of the ancient texts.<3.ra>Hrm...<4.pa> This "
"must be what we in the archaeology\n"
"profession refer to as \"a stroke of luck.\"<5.pa> Er, not\n"
"that I believe in any such thing...<6.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: raw
msgctxt "talk31"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Huh.<2.pa> The mystery deepens...<3.ra>My only response can be to "
"redouble\n"
"my efforts—now that the shrine is\n"
"visible—to solve the mystery at last!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: text_size
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (long)
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: choice
#. 6: text_size
msgctxt "talk32"
msgid ""
"<1.te_si><2.so>\"When a dark light resides in the cursed\n"
"statue's eyes, pierce its gaze to purge\n"
"the seal from the shrine.\"<3.pa>\n"
"The answer is here somewhere...<4.pa>but what is it?<5.ch><6.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound2
#. 3: raw
msgctxt "talk33"
msgid ""
"<1.so><2.so>You again... You certainly look pleased\n"
"with yourself.<3.ra>But no matter. It's time I headed out for\n"
"some more shrine fieldwork. "
msgstr ""

