"things spill.<2.pa> This is just between us,\n"
"understand.\n"
"<3.so>\"When a dark light resides in the cursed\n"
"statue's eyes, pierce its gaze to purge\n"
"the seal from the shrine.\"<4.pa>\n"
"I'm still in the process of deciphering\n"
"that one, so I don't suppose there's\n"
"any harm in sharing it with you.\n"
"That's my life:<5.pa> days spent researching\n"
"shrines and nights filled with the study\n"
"of ancient texts. <6.pa>Back to work now..."
msgstr ""

